msgid ""
"This plugin allows to accept transfer payments through the Online banking."
msgstr ""
"Este plugin permite aceptar pagos en tiempo real por Transferencia Online."

#: inespay.php:257
msgid ""
"To use this payment method in your production online store, you must use  "
"the Real Environment credentials. "
